v AD vung gc vi BC ti H.',1,3.0000000,0.0000000,'essay',1,'dongda.hocmai.com+210907101147+eMvxWG','dongda.hocmai.com+210907101147+7KThbv',0,1631009507,1631009507,3,3,NULL),(5167,342,0,'1839_TL_c3_ B 5 Tinh chat ba ng phan giac cua tam giac_TH_004','Cho $$ \\Delta ABC $$ vung ti C. Tia phn gic BK ca gc ABC (K thuc AC), t K k KE vung gc vi AB (E thuc AB).<br /> a) Chng minh $$ CK=KE $$ .<br /> b) Tia BC ct tia EK ti M. So snh MK v KE.<br /> c) Chng minh CE // MA.',1,'<img src=\"https://hocmai.vn/file.php/1839/toan 7/chuong 3/c3_b05_c4.png\"  alt=\"\"  title=\"\"  border=\"0\"  hspace=\"0\"  vspace=\"0\" /><br /> a) V BK l tia phn gic ca $$ \\widehat{CAB} $$ ; $$ KC\\bot BC,\\,\\,KE\\bot AB $$ nn theo tnh cht (nh l 1) ca im thuc tia phn gic<br /> $$ \\Rightarrow \\,KC=KE. $$ <br /> b) Xt $$ \\Delta MCK $$ vung ti C ta c MK l cnh huyn<br /> nn $$ MK&gt;CK $$ . M<br /> $$ CK=KE $$ (chng minh trn)<br /> $$ \\Rightarrow \\,\\,MK&gt;KE $$ .<br /> c) Xt $$ \\Delta BCK $$ v $$ \\Delta BEK $$ c:<br /> $$ \\widehat{BCK}=\\widehat{BEK}={{90}^{o}} $$ ;<br /> cnh BK chung ; $$ CK=EK $$ <br /> $$ \\Rightarrow \\,\\,\\Delta BCK\\,=\\Delta BEK\\, $$ (cnh huyn, cnh gc vung)<br /> $$ \\Rightarrow \\,\\,BC=BE $$ (1) $$ \\Rightarrow \\,\\Delta BCE $$ cn ti B $$ \\Rightarrow \\,\\,\\widehat{BCE}=\\widehat{BEC} $$ .<br /> Xt $$ \\Delta MCK $$ v $$ \\Delta AEK $$ c:<br /> $$ \\widehat{MCK}=\\widehat{AEK}={{90}^{o}} $$ ; $$ CK=KE\\, $$ ;<br /> $$ \\widehat{CKM}=\\widehat{AKE} $$ (i nh)<br /> $$ \\Rightarrow \\,\\,\\Delta MCK=\\Delta AEK $$ (g. c. g)<br /> $$ \\Rightarrow \\,\\,MC=AE $$ . (2)<br /> Ta c: $$ AB=BE+EA\\,;\\,BM=BC+CM $$ . (3)<br /> T (1) (2) v (3) suy ra $$ AB=BM\\,\\,\\Rightarrow \\,\\,\\Delta ABM $$ cn ti B<br /> $$ \\Rightarrow \\,\\,\\widehat{BMA}=\\widehat{BAM} $$ .<br /> Trong $$ \\Delta ABM $$ c: $$ \\widehat{BAM}+\\widehat{BMA}+\\widehat{ABM}={{180}^{o}} $$ $$ \\Rightarrow \\,\\,2\\widehat{BMA}={{180}^{o}}-\\widehat{ABM} $$ . (4)<br /> Trong $$ \\Delta BCE $$ c:<br /> $$ \\widehat{BCE}+\\widehat{BEC}+\\widehat{CBE}={{180}^{o}} $$ $$ \\Rightarrow \\,\\,2\\widehat{BCE}={{180}^{o}}-\\widehat{CBE}={{180}^{o}}-\\widehat{ABM} $$ .(5)<br /> T (4) v (5) suy ra $$ \\widehat{BMA}=\\widehat{BCE} $$ , m hai gc ny  v tr ng v nn CE // AM.',1,3.0000000,0.0000000,'essay',1,'dongda.hocmai.com+210907101147+FCPTHt','dongda.hocmai.com+210907101147+omitXb',0,1631009507,1631009507,3,3,NULL),(5168,342,0,'1839_TL_c3_ B 5 Tinh chat ba ng phan giac cua tam giac_TH_005','Cho $$ \\widehat{xOy}={{60}^{o}} $$ , im M nm trong gc gc  v cch Ox, Oy mt khng bng 4cm. Tnh  di on thng OM.',1,'<img src=\"https://hocmai.vn/file.php/1839/toan 7/chuong 3/c3_b05_c5.png\"  alt=\"\"  title=\"\"  border=\"0\"  hspace=\"0\"  vspace=\"0\" /><br /> V im M cch u hai cnh Ox, Oy mt khong
