INSERT INTO `omo_question` VALUES (9174,674,0,'tugiac_otc1_c09','<br /> Cho hnh thang ABCD (\\[AB//CD\\] ). Gi E, F theo th t l trung im ca AB, CD. Gi O l trung im ca EF. Qua O v ng thng song song vi AB, ct AD v BC theo th t ti M v N.<br /> a) T gic EMFN l hnh g?<br /> b) Hnh thang ABCD c thm iu kin g  EMFN l hnh thoi.<br /> c) Hnh thang ABCD c thm iu kin g  EMFN l hnh vung.',1,'<div><img src=\"https://hocmai.vn/file.php/1836/Anh/Anh_bai_giang/nh/9otc1.png\"  alt=\"\"  title=\"\"  border=\"0\"  hspace=\"0\"  vspace=\"0\"  width=\"541\"  height=\"291\" /><br /></div> a) Xet hinh thang AEFD co O la trung im EF, \\[OM//AE//DF\\] nn M la trung im AD. Chng minh tng t N la trung im BC.<br /> Ta co<br /> OM la ng trung binh hinh thang AEFD nn $$ OM=\\frac{AE+DF}{2} $$ <br /> Tng t $$ ON=\\frac{EB+FC}{2} $$ <br /> Vi \\[EA=EB,FD=FC\\] nn OM=ON. Do o O la trung im MN. Kt hp k O la trung im EF nn EMFN la hinh binh hanh.<br /> b)<br /> EMFN la hinh thoi khi \\[EM=EN. \\]<br /> EM la ng trung binh tam giac ABD, EN la ng trung binh tam giac BAC nn \\[EM=\\frac{1}{2}DB,\\] \\[EN=\\frac{1}{2}AC. \\] Do o \\[EM=EN\\] khi va chi khi \\[AC=BD\\] , tc ABCD la hinh thang cn.<br /> c) EMFN la hinh vung khi \\[EM=EN\\] va EM vung goc vi EN, tc la ABCD la hinh thang cn va AC vung goc vi BD.',1,0.0000000,0.0000000,'essay',1,'dongda.hocmai.com+210907133729+TpiuDI','dongda.hocmai.com+210907133729+vaxz1b',0,1631021849,1631021849,3,3,NULL),(9175,674,0,'tugiac_otc1_c10','<br /> Cho tam gic ABC vung ti A vi \\[AB=AC=a\\] .<br /> a) Ly im D trn cnh AC v im E trn cnh AB sao cho \\[AD=AE\\] . Cc ng thng vung gc vi EC v t A v D ln lt ct cnh BC  K v L. Chng minh \\[BK=KL. \\]<br /> b) Mt hnh ch nht APMN thay i c nh P trn cnh AB, nh N trn cnh AC v c chu vi lun bng $$ 2\\text{a} $$ . im M di chuyn trn ng no?',1,'<div><img src=\"https://hocmai.vn/file.php/1836/Anh/Anh_bai_giang/nh/10otc1.png\"  alt=\"\"  title=\"\"  border=\"0\"  hspace=\"0\"  vspace=\"0\"  width=\"374\"  height=\"648\" /><br /></div> a