INSERT INTO `omo_question` VALUES (15979,1204,0,'dau_hieu_nhan_biet_tiep_tuyen_cua_duong_tron_03','<b></b>Cho tam gic ABC c hai ng cao BD v CE ct nhau ti H.<br /> a) Chng minh rng bn im A, D, H, E cng nm trn mt ng trn (gi tm ca n l O).<br /> b) Gi M l trung im ca BC. Chng minh rng ME l tip tuyn ca ng trn (O).<br />',1,'<br /><img src=\"https://hocmai.vn/file.php/1042/Anh_chuong_2_Duong_tron/bai_5/cau_3.PNG\"  alt=\"cau 3 bai 5\"  title=\"cau 3 bai 5\"  border=\"0\"  hspace=\"0\"  vspace=\"0\"  width=\"251\"  height=\"230\" /><br /> a) Gi $$ O $$ l trung im ca $$ AH $$ <br /> Tam gic $$ ADH $$ vung ti $$ D $$ <br /> $$ \\Rightarrow OA=OH=OD $$ (Trong tam gic vung ng trung tuyn ng vi cnh huyn c  di bng mt na cnh huyn) $$ \\left( 1 \\right) $$ <br /> Chng minh tng t ta c: $$ OA=OE=OH $$ $$ \\left( 2 \\right) $$ <br /> T (1) v (2) suy ra: Bn im $$ A,E,H,D $$ nm trn ng trn tm $$ O $$ ng knh $$ AH. $$ <br /> b) Ta c: $$ OE=OA\\Rightarrow \\Delta OEA $$ cn ti $$ O\\Rightarrow \\widehat{OEA}=\\widehat{OAE} $$ <br /> M $$ \\widehat{OAE}=\\widehat{HCM} $$ v cng ph vi gc $$ \\widehat{ABC} $$ <br /> Mt khc: $$ \\widehat{HCM}=\\widehat{HEM} $$ (V tam gic $$ MEC $$ cn ti $$ M $$ )<br /> $$ \\Rightarrow \\widehat{OEA}=\\widehat{OAE}=\\widehat{HCM}=\\widehat{HEM} $$ <br /> $$ \\Rightarrow \\widehat{HEM}+\\widehat{HEO}=\\widehat{AEO}+\\widehat{HEO}=\\widehat{HEA}={{90}^{0}} $$ <br /> $$ \\Rightarrow ME\\bot EO\\Rightarrow ME $$ l tip tuyn ca $$ \\left( O \\right) $$',1,1.0000000,0.0000000,'essay',1,'dongda.hocmai.com+210907153947+iy3Alc','dongda.hocmai.com+210907153947+gvcHGW',0,1631029187,1631029187,3,3,NULL),(15980,1204,0,'dau_hieu_nhan_biet_tiep_tuyen_cua_duong_tron_04','<b></b>Cho ng trn (O; R) ng knh AB. V dy AC sao cho $$ \\widehat{CAB}={{30}^{0}} $$ . Trn tia i ca tia BA, ly im M sao cho BM = R. Chng minh rng MC l tip tuyn ca ng trn (O).<br />',1,'<img src=\"https://hocmai.vn/file.php/1042/Anh_chuong_2_Duong_tron/bai_5/cau_4.PNG\"  alt=\"cau 4 bai 5\"  title=\"cau 4 bai 5\"  border=\"0\"  hspace=\"0\"  vspace=\"0\"  width=\"285\"  height=\"162\" /><br /><br /> Tam gic $$ ACB $$ c $$ OC=OA=OB=R $$ <br /> $$ \\Rightarrow \\Delta ACB $$ vung ti $$ C $$ (<span>tam gic c trung tuyn ng vi mt cnh bng na cnh  th tam gic y l tam gic vung</span>)<br /> V $$ \\widehat{CAB}+\\widehat{CBA}={{90}^{0}}\\Rightarrow \\widehat{CBA}={{90}^{0}}-\\widehat{CAB}={{90}^{0}}-{{30}^{0}}={{60}^{0}} $$ <br /> Tam gic $$ OBC $$ c $$ \\left\\{ \\begin{array}{l}<br /> OC=OB=R \\\\<br /> \\widehat{CBO}={{60}^{0}} <br /> \\end{array} \\right. \\Rightarrow \\Delta OBC $$ u<br /> $$ \\Rightarrow BC=BO=BM $$ <br /> $$ \\Rightarrow \\Delta OCM $$ vung ti $$ C $$ (<span>tam gic c trung tuyn ng vi mt cnh bng na cnh  th tam gic y l tam gic vung</span>)<br /> $$ \\Rightarrow MC\\bot OC $$ hay $$ MC $$ l tip tuyn ca ng trn $$ \\left( O \\right) $$',1,1.0000000,0.0000000,'essay',1,'dongda.hocmai.com+210907153947+VDWSyv','dongda.hocmai.com+210907153947+onCPnx',0,1631029187,1631029187,3,3,NULL),(15981,1204,0,'dau_hieu_nhan_biet_tiep_tuyen_cua_duong_tron_05','<b></b>Cho tam gic ABC vung ti A. V ng trn (B;BA) v ng trn (C;CA), chng ct nhau ti im D (khc A). Chng minh rng CD l tip tuyn ca ng trn (B).<br />',1,'<br /><img src=\"https://hocmai.vn/file.php/1042/Anh_chuong_2_Duong_tron/bai_5/cau_5.PNG\"  alt=\"cau 5 bai 5\"  title=\"cau 5 bai 5\"  border=\"0\"  hspace=\"0\"  vspace=\"0\"  width=\"245\"  height=\"172\" /><br /> Xt hai tam gic ABC v DBC, ta c:<br /> BA = BD (bn knh ca (B; BA))<br /> CA = CD (bn knh ca (C; CA))<br /> BC chung<br /> Suy ra: $$ \\Delta ABC=\\Delta DBC\\left( c. c. c \\right) $$ <br /> Suy ra: $$ \\widehat{BAC}=\\widehat{BDC} $$ <br /> M $$ \\widehat{BAC}={{90}^{0}} $$ (gi thit) $$ \\Rightarrow \\widehat{BDC}={{90}^{0}}. $$ <br /> Suy ra: $$ CD\\bot BD $$ ti $$ D. $$ <br /> Vy, CD l tip tuyn ca ng trn (B; BA)',1,1.0000000,0.0000000,'essay',1,'dongda.hocmai.com+210907153947+OgMIek','dongda.hocmai.com+210907153947+M3xllb',0,1631029187,1631029187,3,3,NULL),(15982,1